{"tid":2454604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：鍾南山：初步希望內地到7月疫苗接種率達4成","createTime":"2021-03-20T11:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T12:00:04.000Z","uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"27a6bd12fbdb451065e4717d50be6e3bf46d00c0","tid":2454604,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:02:08.000Z","msg":"中國工程院院士鍾南山說，內地目前新冠疫苗接種率較低，只有約百分之4，接種工作要加強，藥廠會加快生產，初步希望到7月接種率最少達到4成。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山在一個網上研討會表示，目前在內地很願意接種疫苗的人不是很多，很多人覺得必要性不大，覺得現時疫情問題不大，態度有所放鬆。<br />\n<br />\n但他指出，內地的疫苗接種率始終要追上，當日後開放給外國人入境，即使外國人已接種疫苗，都不等如完全不受感染，都可以是帶病毒的人，可以令到內地人受感染。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山說，<strong>有歐洲國家曾經提出透過自然感染再建立群體免疫，現時情況反映這是不現實、不科學及不人道</strong>，現在是要靠大規模疫苗接種。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他認為，<strong>香港採取的封區強制檢測做法是好，正因這方面的努力，令確診數字下降</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581648-20210320.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581648-20210320.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=1de71bd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581648-20210320.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=084dfd24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581648-20210320.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a26fba4aca678b844ac3d354c6743255a7c85fad","tid":2454604,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NBxG0aF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNBxG0aF.png&h=6efc1d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhTyRhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhTyRhk.jpg&h=2e411897&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5387c78a56eaea9ac55714d5866dbe932d7c2dc0","tid":2454604,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"支那人一個二個當疫情完左，采你都傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141c524dcde5d23d83db72e2eee648cda78d3ec5","tid":2454604,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5387c78a56eaea9ac55714d5866dbe932d7c2dc0","tid":2454604,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"支那人一個二個當疫情完左，采你都傻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"係佢哋都唔信自己嘢 試吓話係打biontech睇吓會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a2318659abc50672a2b9d721364ec9a751d9cf","tid":2454604,"uid":104447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"關鍵十四天呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326526c613c2d3bacbd0432a41042a0c82c11acb","tid":2454604,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"接晒都係得50%人免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}